Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.03,0:11:03.50,FFF,+,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(127,156)}但你們兩人例外
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.03,0:11:03.50,FFF,+,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(102,125)}零分處理
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.49,0:11:09.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那之後過了一個禮拜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.21,0:11:12.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,課程也正式開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.14,0:11:16.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對還沒熟悉日語的我來說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.88,0:11:19.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現代國語到底在上什麼完全聽不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.17,0:11:22.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤其是對於古典文學 更是難解
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.80,0:11:28.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼久請吉井同學 在這情況下的活用形應該是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.13,0:11:31.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  華麗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.45,0:11:36.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我問你古文的活用形 答案卻回答的京都方言
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.63,0:11:40.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這真是令人愉悅到猴年馬月的回答呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.26,0:11:41.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？啊咧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.92,0:11:59.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼在下次上課前請復習學到現在的內容
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.83,0:12:01.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於完了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.08,0:12:06.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想到總算從拷問般無聊的課堂解放
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.87,0:12:09.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,島田同學 要去哪里呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.13,0:12:11.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有 什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.20,0:12:12.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.84,0:12:14.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 要回家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.73,0:12:16.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 what a sea？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.17,0:12:19.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,wa ta shi （我）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.70,0:12:23.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 原來說了我要回家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.84,0:12:26.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉沒有聽清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.28,0:12:28.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,島田同學是從外國回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.39,0:12:31.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還以為說的是外語呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.26,0:12:40.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於不習慣日語的我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.76,0:12:43.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒能夠挺清楚他說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.99,0:12:46.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要努力去理解
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.67,0:12:48.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是大腦追不上 好像要爆炸一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.72,0:12:52.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為一會還有班會
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.43,0:12:55.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 現在還不能回家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.49,0:13:01.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 再等等就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.62,0:13:05.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙在笑什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.12,0:13:09.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能說日語就這麼有趣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.37,0:13:13.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.96,0:13:25.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在說美波中學的時候參加了什麼社團嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.17,0:13:28.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是現在該問的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.49,0:13:30.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說回來這傢伙的日語
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.17,0:13:31.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和文法合得上嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.60,0:13:43.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.27,0:13:54.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼辦才好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.80,0:13:59.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼大家都不瞭解我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.71,0:14:02.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明這麼努力了的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.84,0:14:01.72,D2,+,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.05,0:14:05.18,D2,+,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來的說 姐姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.40,0:14:09.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說大家都討厭我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.72,0:14:07.35,D2,+,0000,0000,0000,,學校怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.64,0:14:11.27,D2,+,0000,0000,0000,,非常有趣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.64,0:14:14.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我其實不應該來這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.19,0:14:14.19,D2,+,0000,0000,0000,,找到朋友了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.44,0:14:17.19,D2,+,0000,0000,0000,,有很多不錯的朋友哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.44,0:14:18.69,D2,+,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.94,0:14:21.11,D2,+,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 日本真是個好地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.40,0:14:22.53,D2,+,0000,0000,0000,,那真是太好了的說！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.71,0:14:41.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我仍然沒能融入班級之中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.53,0:14:45.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不明白日語 沒法交朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.76,0:14:47.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有談話物件
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.10,0:14:48.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是惡性循環
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.70,0:14:54.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原因是最初的那一天給人印象很差
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.06,0:14:59.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天從弄錯名字的漢字開始
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.47,0:15:09.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 這應該是保持著錯誤的樣子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.14,0:15:10.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.13,0:15:17.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 明久 開物中學出身的傢伙們說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.15,0:15:20.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賭上小賣部麵包來打籃球 你怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.17,0:15:21.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去要去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.26,0:15:23.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個月的伙食費很緊張啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.34,0:15:24.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.74,0:15:26.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也讓老夫來參加吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.99,0:15:28.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來好像很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.64,0:15:31.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些傢伙什麼時候變得這麼要好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.35,0:15:38.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,jyunu budorepa dobuniru monami！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.52,0:15:42.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,jyunu budorepa dobuniru monami！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.52,0:15:47.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊這傢伙 說些不明所以的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.70,0:15:51.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不明白日語啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.83,0:15:53.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來莫娜美是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.79,0:15:55.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是莫娜美而是美波啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.74,0:15:59.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明連我名字都記不住 別套近乎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.77,0:16:03.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,jyunu budorepa dobuniru monoomi
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.14,0:16:07.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,jyunu …
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.99,0:16:09.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別向我搭話 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.70,0:16:11.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別踢我腳？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.80,0:16:14.87,D2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(636,635)}你這傢伙到底多欠操啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.27,0:16:17.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是man, you are？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.60,0:16:20.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是男人啊 那麼難道說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.91,0:16:22.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,島田是個男的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.23,0:16:25.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙連英語都沒法溝通嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.24,0:16:27.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙到底多欠操啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.80,0:16:29.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說對你感到不爽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.24,0:16:31.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.06,0:16:33.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對著憤怒的女生叫她男的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.90,0:16:35.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,膽子不小啊 明久
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.82,0:16:37.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這樣的 島田同學
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.46,0:16:39.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我並不是因為島田童鞋的胸部很小
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.23,0:16:40.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才認為島田同學是個男的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.75,0:16:43.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不過使用常識來想的疼啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.93,0:16:46.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不明白日語
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.94,0:16:48.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不知道為什麼只有胸部小
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.74,0:16:50.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一部分清清楚楚的聽到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.39,0:16:53.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙到底多欠操啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.39,0:16:57.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟透了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.82,0:16:59.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的糟透了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.35,0:17:01.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不應該來日本的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.85,0:17:02.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 島田
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.80,0:17:06.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是剛認識那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.23,0:17:07.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.64,0:17:09.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.71,0:17:11.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定是個非常有趣的傢伙哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.63,0:17:13.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Baka
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.90,0:17:19.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙說的話 去查查吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.13,0:17:43.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊是說笨蛋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.60,0:17:45.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事情我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.92,0:17:51.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,jyunu budorepa到底是什麼意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.44,0:17:54.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是在把我當傻子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.99,0:17:59.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去查查那傢伙在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.51,0:18:01.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後再去戲弄那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.57,0:18:05.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,jyunu budorepa
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.10,0:18:07.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,jyunu budorepa
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.47,0:18:09.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,jyunu budorepa
